# ④ root_dir/.htaccess（サンプル）

```apache
RewriteEngine On

# Block direct access to admin directory
RewriteRule ^admin/ - [F]

# Route all requests to admin/index.php
RewriteRule ^.*$ admin/index.php [L]

# ---- IP restriction ----
<RequireAll>
  Require all denied

  # Example allowed IP
  Require ip 203.0.113.10
</RequireAll>
